《用力爱我》由[[马克斯·马丁|马克斯·马丁]]、[[沙凡·科提查|沙凡·科提查]]、{{tsl|en|Peter Svensson|彼得·斯文森}}、{{tsl|en|Ali Payami|阿里·帕亚米}}、[[威肯|亚伯·特斯法耶]]、{{tsl|en|Belly (rapper)|贝利|艾哈迈德·巴尔舍}}共同创作，由帕亚米和{{tsl|en|Carolina Liar|卡罗莱纳骗子|彼得·卡尔松}}制作，斯文森同时担任配唱制作人。歌曲是一首爱莉安娜与威肯合作演唱的二重唱曲。根据{{tsl|en|Kobalt Music Group|Kobalt音乐集团}}在Musicnotes.com上发布的乐谱，歌曲是以[[C|C#]][[调|小调]]谱写，[[速度_(音樂)|速度]]为每分钟100拍。爱莉安娜的演唱音域为[[F_(音名)|E<sub>3</sub>]]至[[E_(音名)|E<sub>5</sub>]]。<ref>{{cite web|title=Ariana Grande - "Love Me Harder" - Digital Sheet Music|url=http://www.musicnotes.com/sheetmusic/mtd.asp?ppn=MN0140604|publisher=Musicnotes.com|accessdate=2016-03-23|archive-date=2016-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160613014802/http://www.musicnotes.com/sheetmusic/mtd.asp?ppn=MN0140604|dead-url=no}}</ref>该是一首[[合成器流行|合成器流行]]与[[当代节奏布鲁斯|节奏布鲁斯]]结合的情歌，<ref>{{cite news|title=New Music: Ariana Grande f/ The Weeknd – 'Love Me Harder'|url=http://www.rap-up.com/2014/08/20/new-music-ariana-grande-f-the-weeknd-love-me-harder/|accessdate=2016-03-28|work={{tsl|en|Rap-Up||Rap-Up}}|date=2014-08-20|archive-date=2015-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150915042229/http://www.rap-up.com/2014/08/20/new-music-ariana-grande-f-the-weeknd-love-me-harder/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="complex">{{cite web |last=Ortiz |first=Edwin |url=http://www.complex.com/music/2014/12/best-songs-2014/ariana-grande-love-me-harder |title=Ariana Grande f/ the Weeknd "Love Me Harder" – The 50 Best Songs of 2014 |work={{tsl|en|Complex (magazine)|Complex}} |date=2014-12-08 |accessdate=2015-09-07 |archive-date=2015-10-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151001052718/http://www.complex.com/music/2014/12/best-songs-2014/ariana-grande-love-me-harder |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="latimes"/><ref name=ballad>{{cite news|last1=Bacle|first1=Ariana|title=Ariana Grande and The Weeknd pair up for 'Love Me Harder' video|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2014/11/03/ariana-grande-weeknd-love-me-harder-video|accessdate=2016-03-30|work=[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]|date=2014-11-03|archive-date=2016-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160315030031/http://www.ew.com/article/2014/11/03/ariana-grande-weeknd-love-me-harder-video|dead-url=no}}</ref>歌曲以柔和的电子背景音开始，之后转为“‘令人躁动’的强烈电音节拍”<ref name="popjustice">{{cite news|last1=Cragg|first1=Michael|title=Ariana Grande’s ‘My Everything’: A first listen review thing|url=https://www.popjustice.com/briefing/guests/ariana-grandes-my-everything-a-first-listen-review-thing/|accessdate=2016-03-28|work={{tsl|en|Popjustice||Popjustice}}|date=2014-08-18|archive-date=2016-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160410032628/http://www.popjustice.com/briefing/guests/ariana-grandes-my-everything-a-first-listen-review-thing/|dead-url=no}}</ref>与一段吉他[[固定音型|重复乐段]],<ref name="billboardreview"/>同时“大太空风格的电子音效”贯穿始终。<ref name="popjustice"/>与此同时，来自《公告牌》的理查德·S.·何将歌曲描述为“一首激情四溢的合成器浪潮与节奏布鲁斯结合的歌曲，打着色情的擦边球 - 并且这样更加诱人”。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/8390286/ariana-grande-every-song-ranked|title=Every Ariana Grande Song, Ranked: Critic's Picks|work=Billboard|access-date=2018-08-09|archive-date=2019-11-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191119173308/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/8390286/ariana-grande-every-song-ranked|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[官方榜单公司|官方榜单公司]]的罗布·科普西表示歌曲使他联想到[[德雷克_(歌手)|德雷克]]那些“最富有情感”的歌曲，像是2010年《{{tsl|en|Find Your Love}}》和2013年的《{{tsl|en|Hold On, We're Going Home}}》，<ref name="officialcharts"/>同时杂志《[[Time_Out|Time Out]]》的尼克·列文把歌曲称作是“[[蘿蘋|蘿蘋]]和[[瑪麗亞·凱莉|瑪麗亞·凱莉]]的交融”。<ref name=Robyn>{{cite news|last1=Levine|first1=Nick|title=Ariana Grande – 'My Everything' album review|url=http://www.timeout.com/london/music/ariana-grande-my-everything-album-review?zone_id=63887&page_number=4|accessdate=2016-03-29|work=[[Time_Out|Time Out]]|date=2014-08-26|archive-date=2016-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160415142041/http://www.timeout.com/london/music/ariana-grande-my-everything-album-review?zone_id=63887&page_number=4|dead-url=no}}</ref>

爱莉安娜在歌词中表达了她对爱情的渴望，<ref name="billboardreview"/>充满了关于[[BDSM|虐恋]]的[[双关语|双关语]]。<ref name="latimes"/>在歌曲的开始，爱莉安娜想要一个男人“无论在呼吸时、快乐时、遭受痛苦时还是幸福时都能完全满足她的要求，”唱到：“Baby, in that moment, you'll know this is/Something bigger than us and beyond bliss.”<ref name="pluggedin">{{cite web|last1=Holz|first1=Adam R.|title="Love Me Harder" Track Review (2014)|url=http://www.pluggedin.com/music-reviews/track/ariana-grande-love-me-harder/|publisher={{tsl|en|Plugged In}}. {{tsl|en|Focus on the Family}}|accessdate=2016-03-28|archive-date=2016-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160414052416/http://www.pluggedin.com/music-reviews/track/ariana-grande-love-me-harder/|dead-url=no}}</ref>在歌曲副歌中，她告诉她的暧昧对象，如果他真的想要拥有她，就不能把爱情看做一场游戏，<ref name="complex"/>警告道：“'Cause if you want to keep me, you gotta, gotta, gotta, gotta, got to love me harder/And if you really need me, you gotta, gotta, gotta, gotta, got to love me harder.”<ref name="pluggedin"/>之后，威肯扮演了一名暗恋者，<ref name="fact"/>演唱了有关“与女人发生性行为时的感受，”以及“肉体承诺”的歌词，<ref name="pluggedin"/>唱道：“Can you feel the pressure between your hips/ I’ll make you feel like the first time.”<ref name="officialcharts"/>在歌曲的桥段，“爱莉安娜和威肯互相回应歌词‘oohs’。”<ref name="complex"/>

