歌曲在发行后获得了一致赞赏。音乐网站[[Allmusic|Allmusic]]的{{tsl|en|Stephen Thomas Erlewine|斯蒂芬·托马斯·厄勒温}}表示威肯在歌曲中“抢占“了爱莉安娜的风头。<ref name="allmusic">{{cite web|last1=Erlewine|first1=Stephen Thomas|author-link=Stephen Thomas Erlewine|title=My Everything - Ariana Grande - Songs, Reviews, Credits - AllMusic|url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/my-everything-mw0002698499|publisher=[[Allmusic|Allmusic]]. [[All_Media_Guide|All Media Network]]|accessdate=2016-03-28|archive-date=2014-08-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140829165315/http://www.allmusic.com/album/my-everything-mw0002698499|dead-url=no}}</ref>杂志《[[告示牌_(雜誌)|公告牌]]》的杰森·李普舒特表示“两人的合作很理智，”并称赞了威肯“非常真挚的吟唱”。<!-- and the "driving guitar riff" for being "delicious 80's cheese".--><ref name="billboardreview">{{cite news|last1=Lipshut|first1=Jason|title=Ariana Grande Expands on 'My Everything': Track-By-Track Review|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/review/6229287/ariana-grande-my-everything-billboard-album-review|accessdate=2016-03-28|work=Billboard|date=2014-08-25|archive-date=2018-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180625133909/https://www.billboard.com/articles/review/6229287/ariana-grande-my-everything-billboard-album-review|dead-url=no}}</ref>《[[洛杉矶时报|洛杉矶时报]]》的迈克·伍德称这是一首“让人们无法想象，一位仅有21岁、周知为大家闺秀的歌手所演唱的一首黑暗风（并且更充分体现）节奏布鲁斯的本名曲。<ref name="latimes">{{cite web|last1=Wood|first1=Mikael|title=Review: Ariana Grande makes big things happen on 'My Everything'|url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/music/posts/la-et-ms-review-ariana-grande-makes-big-things-happen-on-my-everything-20140829-story.html|work=Los Angeles Times|date=2014-08-29|access-date=2017-03-18|archive-date=2014-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006215304/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/music/posts/la-et-ms-review-ariana-grande-makes-big-things-happen-on-my-everything-20140829-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>《[[卫报|卫报]]》的{{tsl|en|Kitty Empire|奇提·艾姆派尔}}写道歌曲“饱满，中板的气氛”使其脱颖而出，并称威肯在歌曲中“并没有在其中掺杂过多自己的风格，但依然保持了他精彩的演唱，同时，爱莉安娜很好的保持了自己的风格。”<ref>{{cite web|last1=Empire|first1=Kitty|title=Ariana Grande: My Everything review – every so often a little shard of personality pierces the sheen|url=https://www.theguardian.com/music/2014/aug/24/my-everything-ariana-grande-review-slick-expensive-album|website=The Guardian|date=2014-08-23|access-date=2017-03-18|archive-date=2016-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161211183840/https://www.theguardian.com/music/2014/aug/24/my-everything-ariana-grande-review-slick-expensive-album|dead-url=no}}</ref>《[[前音後果|前音後果]]》的米歇尔·格拉尼称这首歌“十分具有感染力”，称两人的合作“简直是天生一对——爱莉安娜柔软的嗓音与威肯老练的低音很好的衬托了对方的声音。”<ref name="consequence">{{cite news|last1=Geslani|first1=Michelle|title=Listen: Ariana Grande’s "Love Me Harder" featuring The Weeknd|url=http://consequenceofsound.net/2014/08/listen-ariana-grandes-love-me-harder-featuring-the-weeknd/|accessdate=2016-03-28|publisher=《[[前音後果|前音後果]]》|date=2014-08-20|archive-date=2016-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160417051715/http://consequenceofsound.net/2014/08/listen-ariana-grandes-love-me-harder-featuring-the-weeknd/|dead-url=no}}</ref>音乐网站{{tsl|en|Idolator (website)|Idolator}}的布拉德利·斯特恩写道，歌曲是“一首使人无法抵挡的电子流行作品”，<ref name="idolator">{{cite news|last1=Stern|first1=Bradley|title=Ariana Grande Streams 4 Songs From ‘My Everything’: Listen To "Why Try," "A Little Bit Of Your Heart," "Be My Baby" & "Love Me Harder"|url=http://www.idolator.com/7531793/ariana-grande-streams-4-songs-from-my-everything-listen-to-why-try-a-little-bit-of-your-heart-be-my-baby-love-me-harder|accessdate=2016-03-28|publisher=Idolator|date=2014-08-20}}</ref>同时卡罗琳·门尼斯非常喜欢两人的组合，认为“这两个人的歌声的结合堪称完美”。<ref name="musictimes">{{cite news|last1=Menyes|first1=Carolyn|title=Junk Mail: Ariana Grande 'My Everything' Album Review Via Email|url=http://www.musictimes.com/articles/9337/20140827/junk-mail-ariana-grande-everything-album-review-via-email.htm|accessdate=2016-03-28|publisher=Music Times|date=2014-08-27|archive-date=2016-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160319234301/http://www.musictimes.com/articles/9337/20140827/junk-mail-ariana-grande-everything-album-review-via-email.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

